#: ../../../../../Wrapping/Python/vtkmodules/gtk/GtkGLExtVTKRenderWindowInteractor.py:9
msgid ""
"Provides a pyGtk vtkRenderWindowInteractor widget.  This embeds a   "
"vtkRenderWindow inside a GTK widget and uses the   "
"vtkGenericRenderWindowInteractor for the event handling.  This is   similar "
"to GtkVTKRenderWindowInteractor.py."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../../Wrapping/Python/vtkmodules/gtk/GtkGLExtVTKRenderWindowInteractor.py:14
msgid ""
"The extensions here allow the use of gtkglext rather than gtkgl and   "
"pygtk-2 rather than pygtk-0.  It requires pygtk-2.0.0 or later."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../../Wrapping/Python/vtkmodules/gtk/GtkGLExtVTKRenderWindowInteractor.py:17
msgid "There is a working example at the bottom."
msgstr ""

