#: ../../../../../Wrapping/Python/vtkmodules/gtk/GtkGLExtVTKRenderWindowInteractor.py:21
msgid ""
"John Hunter <jdhunter@ace.bsd.uchicago.edu> developed and tested   this code "
"based on VTK's GtkVTKRenderWindow.py and extended it to   work with "
"pygtk-2.0.0."
msgstr ""

